    the response "_Created with [AIPRM Prompt "Create Key Points + Blog Post"](https://www.aiprm.com/prompts/copywriting/summarize/2007522288979402752/)_"
    --- [TARGETLANGUAGE] Please write in english [PROMPT] Remove line breaks, any
    unneeded punctuation, and repetition from the following transcript. Include the
    revised transcript, labeled "Video transcript". Place this revised "transcript"
    after the "summary" described below. Summarize the "video transcript" in a short
    summary paragraph followed by a bullet point list to highlight the "Key Points".
    Do not refer to "the speaker". Instead, write from the first person directly to
    the reader. Separate the first sentence of the summary paragraphy from the rest
    of the paragraph with a line break and include the text "INSERT VIDEO" on a line
    between the first and following sentences. Address the reader directly with phrases
    like "your" website. Begin the first sentence of the summary with "The video below
    describes...". In the next section labeled "blog post" create a blog post from
    the Video Transcript. Use bold text for title of the blog and h2 format for subheadings.
    Include a section labeled blog post details after the title of the blog and before
    the text of the blog. Include a meta description with fewer than 150 characters.'
